In answer to the previous post, nothing is going to give you a similar flavor to cilantro. However, if you jsut want to add some color, you could add flat leaf parsley, although in a lesser amount. For flavor I would sub fresh basil, as it is very common in Thai recipes...maybe half parsley and half basil?

